# Sample values for generating a greenfield prompt pack.

REPO_PATH=/path/to/my-greenfield-app
PROJECT_NAME=Market Pulse Console
PRINCIPLE_1=Keep the first release narrow, operator-facing, and production-oriented.
PRINCIPLE_2=Validate all inbound and outbound contracts at runtime.
PRINCIPLE_3=Do not create implementation tasks without explicit verification criteria.
PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION=An internal web app that surfaces live market alerts, analyst notes, and replayable decision history for a small trading desk.
IN_SCOPE_1=Operator login, dashboard shell, and alert feed.
IN_SCOPE_2=Historical search for alerts and analyst notes with filters.
IN_SCOPE_3=Basic team management for inviting and disabling users.
OUT_OF_SCOPE_1=Automated trade execution.
OUT_OF_SCOPE_2=Mobile-native applications.
OUT_OF_SCOPE_3=Multi-tenant billing or subscription management.
